{
  "texts": [
    "For each author, we computed the maximum DI across their articles.",
    "Finally, we computed the percentile of the obtained value across articles to compute the disruptiveness of an author.To measure the impact of a work, we used two methods.",
    "First, for each author i, we computed the maximum number of citations ĉi received by any of their articles across their career.",
    "Since citation counts are distributed with a heavy-tailed function, we used the transformation log(ĉ i + 1) to quantify the impact.",
    "In addition, we further quantified the importance of works citing another work by using a more global network measure: the PageRank algorithm."
  ]
}